satellite.heading: Isathelayithi
satellite.specs:
Ubukhulu: 50x58x64 mm
I-1P PocketQube
Isisindo: 245 g
Izinto zokwakha: i-aluminium, igolide, i-fiberglass, nezinto ze-elekthronikhi.
I-Orbit: Ukuphakama 525 ± 25 km; ukuthambekela: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Isiqalisi: I-PSLV (Imoto Yokuqalisa I-Satellite Polar) esetshenziswa yi-ISRO

antenna.heading: I-Antenna/Sculpture
antenna.specs:
Ubukhulu: 6 m (ububanzi) futhi 1.2m (ubude)
Isisindo: 46 kg
Izinto: i-aluminium, ibhodi elinesibuko se-epoxy, idome le-aluminium yegolide elimiswe ngesakhiwo sesikafula.

radio.heading: I-Radio Specs
radio.specs:
Isixhumanisi esiphansi: 468.5 MHz
Ukuguquguquka: CSS
Umkhawulokudonsa: TBD
